[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man suffers head injury during assault in Belfast city centre

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man in his 30s is in a serious condition in hospital after suffering a head injury during an assault in Belfast city centre.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
An altercation broke out between two men inside a fast food outlet about 00:35 BST on Sunday which then continued outside.
Police said the suspect is described being aged in his early 20s, of slim to medium build, with cropped dark hair shaved on both sides.
Police have appealed for information.
